Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅德叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,離開科西嘉已經10年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼時候回到巴黎的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得很多東西都很懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,姊夫是個偉大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,洛朗．布克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅讓組織團結\N{\fs8}\N{\r}也對家人很體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果姊夫沒發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟妳也不會\N{\fs8}\N{\r}從科西嘉被趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還在做那個工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要在巴黎工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊﹐我是那麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父母遭到殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,布克家與組織因此而瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,科西嘉被敵對組織\N{\fs8}\N{\r}納入了勢力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,無處可去的我\N{\fs8}\N{\r}跟著克羅德叔叔離開了家鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅德．費得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是我媽媽那邊的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前曾受過他的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他不但陪我玩\N{\fs8}\N{\r}而且還教我如何工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐他是位很嚴格的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有機會我再介紹給妳認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不知道索達的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果叔叔知道\N{\fs8}\N{\r}他一定會跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真高興妳見到妳叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,馬賽那邊怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你那邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還記得那座湖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,以前叔叔帶我去過的湖是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剛來巴黎的時候\N{\fs8}\N{\r}我一直開心不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔總是為我加油打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要再去一次那座湖？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？不想去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知不知道什麼\N{\fs8}\N{\r}關於“NOlR”的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的“NOlR”就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你為什麼要問我這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有﹐妳不知道就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對﹐沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知不知道什麼\N{\fs8}\N{\r}關於“NOlR”的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才送來了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是叔叔寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是叔叔種的花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真為妳感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨﹐讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,費得﹐真高興看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很有精神嘛﹐迪波瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了﹐沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候回來巴黎的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你未免太見外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要回來為什麼不早點通知我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有很多雜事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,憑你的能力\N{\fs8}\N{\r}應該會有很多工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說﹐我也是有事想拜託你\N{\fs8}\N{\r}所以才找你出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這陣子連續發生了一些\N{\fs8}\N{\r}詭異的兇殺案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊﹐被殺的都是些重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有些人跟我關係很密切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你幫我查出是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意幫我忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這很簡單﹐根本不需要查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？你知道是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以為你是個\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不懂開玩笑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他們的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字也在他們的委託名單中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你寄來的花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客氣﹐進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只要付出真心照顧\N{\fs8}\N{\r}花也會給予回應的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然也有失敗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我來是為了讓我看花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要對花說話﹐花就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在有件很重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫忙是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不﹐我希望妳不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯﹐就是妳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你會來見我並非偶然對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你一開始就那麼打算了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙了我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也對我說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說妳不知道NOlR
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,本來什麼都不說\N{\fs8}\N{\r}直接殺了她也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐我還是想跟妳先說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,委託人是…索達對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知道他們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔﹐為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還是不要知道比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了我們好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不完成這項工作\N{\fs8}\N{\r}我就會被他們消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就像姊夫那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,洛朗．布克因為違逆了索達\N{\fs8}\N{\r}所以才被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟老婆兒子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔你以前就知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不可以想要去了解索達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我對他們發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不過問理由\N{\fs8}\N{\r}隨時都要遵從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才能活著離開科西嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著妳一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣妳應該明白\N{\fs8}\N{\r}索達有多恐怖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這片葉子沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們比這朵花還要脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被索達纏上\N{\fs8}\N{\r}就絕對無法再逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是誰都沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要重蹈洛朗的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我會帶那孩子來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了以後﹐我們去那座湖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在時期也剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,湖畔景色應該是最美的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,辦點雜事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是叫妳不要跟來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣妳還是要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐﹐要不要我去叫他？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不必了﹐我自己過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法去那座湖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妳果然是洛朗．布克的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:34.46,ED,,0,0,0,,輕輕地被觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:47.11,ED,,0,0,0,,終於察覺到臉頰的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:53.02,ED,,0,0,0,,清晨醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:23:05.40,ED,,0,0,0,,突然開始注意到鳥鳴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.43,ED,,0,0,0,,什麼都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:20.91,ED,,0,0,0,,不知內心追求的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.11,ED,,0,0,0,,總是望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:33.32,ED,,0,0,0,,不知何時開始這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:46.26,ED,,0,0,0,,讓思念朝著雲的下方飛去
